{"tid":2421524,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"LIHKG箍牙討論區38","createTime":"2021-02-24T14:19:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T14:31:14.000Z","uid":377880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6c1048173f1de6c09f8ea81034feb3e434cb8846","tid":2421524,"uid":377880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:19:24.000Z","msg":"箍牙Q&amp;A credit to 施華朗尼馬達巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎一齊集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ：想箍牙，搵邊個好？<br />\nA：一般建議普通科牙醫或者牙齒矯正科專科。<br />\n名單呢到有：<a href=\"https://www.dchk.org.hk/tc/list/list.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dchk.org.hk%2Ftc%2Flist%2Flist.htm&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8AsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=bb961bc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dchk.org.hk/tc/list/list.htm</a><br />\n<br />\nQ：普通科同專科有咩分別？<br />\nA：專科醫生成為普通牙醫後要進修多最少六年，可以處理複雜既牙齒問題，收費亦較貴。<br />\n<br />\nQ：箍牙一般有咩種類揀？<br />\nA：主要有傳統或者透明(隱適美)。<br />\n<br />\nQ：治療費大約幾多，包左D咩？<br />\nA：<br />\n普通科 - 傳統約$30000起，透明(隱適美)約$40000起<br />\n普通科收費一般已包括治療前X光片及牙模，箍牙費，一副固定器，箍牙所需之相關牙科費用(例如：剝牙、補牙、洗牙等)<br />\n專科 - 傳統約$40000起，透明(隱適美)約$50000起<br />\n專科收費一般只包括治療前X光片及牙模，箍牙費，一副固定器<br />\n**個別醫生收費會有不用，詳情請向診所查詢<br />\n<br />\nQ：想開始箍牙、療程係點？<br />\nA：首次諮詢(免費至過千元，部份會於治療費扣除) &gt; 制作矯齒記錄包括X光片、相片及牙模(一千至數千元，一般可以於治療費扣除) &gt; 醫生提供治療計劃(免費) &gt; 展開療程<br />\n<br />\nQ：廿幾歲先黎箍牙，會唔會太遲？<br />\nA：唔少人都係呢個歲數先箍<br />\n<br />\nQ：有咩醫生、診所要小心？<br />\nA：康齒堂、網上遙距箍牙、淘寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n了解更多：20200406【杏林在線】傳統箍牙vs隱形牙套<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SY-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSY-&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8AsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=aec44e66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SY-</a>"},{"pid":"844cf55e56801204c2dd01586440fb9738758e7f","tid":2421524,"uid":377880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:21:48.000Z","msg":"見1001好耐都未開post 所以我嚟開啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"956b46fffa30b9721efd409855a206233d4abc0e","tid":2421524,"uid":51309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T16:25:16.000Z","msg":"啱啱開始上箍 好鐘意每隔幾日就影下棚牙睇下有冇郁到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b626d9490f351ff7bf5b5ae0cb3f90a5a58bcb7f","tid":2421524,"uid":175264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T02:52:01.000Z","msg":"箍緊隱適美嗰間最近介紹人去好似有平 有無人有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b589e672a8a569633fc5ba2e0dc94a2e7bd893dd","tid":2421524,"uid":143474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T03:12:39.000Z","msg":"retainer brite 同 orthokey 邊到有現貨買<br />\n廢時上網買<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026754a174b15d672388e47c696d43aacb1b97b5","tid":2421524,"uid":16853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b626d9490f351ff7bf5b5ae0cb3f90a5a58bcb7f","tid":2421524,"uid":175264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T02:52:01.000Z","msg":"箍緊隱適美嗰間最近介紹人去好似有平 有無人有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:28:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4091f5ef9a61e5846cb91846607d3127154fb2f3","tid":2421524,"uid":46053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:42:54.000Z","msg":"想問下大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我箍隱適美，剝左上下共四隻牙，<br />\n上排牙窿整左好耐先埋晒口，<br />\n到最後上兩星期check 果陣，<br />\n牙醫用牙線check ，<br />\n啲牙全部都有痴埋一齊，<br />\n即係牙中間再無&quot;喇&quot;，咁終於都搞掂啦。<br />\n<br />\n而家帶左兩星期retainer <br />\n我今日食完野用牙線時發現，<br />\n上排剝牙果兩個位啲牙<br />\n同側邊啲牙無connect，<br />\n即係牙線一下就入左去，<br />\n完全無kick 住嘅應覺<br />\n點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上排呢兩個位搞左我好耐，<br />\n我應唔應該即刻同牙醫講？<br />\n定係等佢九個月後定期檢查先講？<br />\n我驚到時佢話可以再整但又要收錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但又驚佢愈來愈大<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e55fd6103326c900e594a8bc91433263238bfde","tid":2421524,"uid":67197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:29:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"512f31f1f9353ec31f48ae754d106cf1e5067134","tid":2421524,"uid":347989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T14:31:14.000Z","msg":"有冇人箍過荃灣韓雋疇？"}]}